text: Reinøya may refer to: * Reinøya, Troms – an island in the Karlsøy municipality in Troms * Reinøya, Vardø – an island in the Vardø municipality in Finnmark * Reinøya, Porsanger – an island in the Porsanger municipality in Finnmark * Reinøya, Sør-Varanger – an island in the Sør-Varanger municipality in Finnmark * Reinøya, Måsøy – an island in the Måsøy municipality in Finnmark
title: Reinøya
